{
  "text": "The inclusion of cultural activities for healthcare staff may offer a cheap and therefore sustainable way to receive these multiple benefits. Cultural activities may therefore be valuable in planning strategically for the prevention of stress and in enabling the creation of sustainable healthcare systems [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "154965184"
